.Dd July 27, 2016
.Dt XSCREENSHOT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm xscreenshot
.Nd simple screenshot utility
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Ar winid
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
makes a screenshot of the screen or a window with id
.Ar winid
and writes image data in the Farbfeld format to stdout.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Ar winid
the window id, can be in decimal or hexadecimal format.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr xprop 1 ,
.Xr xwininfo 1
